# Pin Go source to LF on every OS so gofmt and CI never trip on CRLF.
# This repo is checked out on Windows with core.autocrlf=true and had no
# .gitattributes, which made `gofmt -l` flag every .go file (the blobs are
# already LF; only the working tree was CRLF) and fail the format gate.
# Broader text/eol normalization is tracked as a follow-up.
* text=auto
*.go text eol=lf

# Binaries: never normalize.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.gz binary
*.zip binary
